<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/tulip-siddiq> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Tulip Siddiq was Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury and City Minister) at HM Treasury from 9 July 2024 to 14 January 2025. She was elected as the MP for Hampstead and Highgate in July 2024."@en .
